Taking Governor's collection
A thief nicknamed Baldie hid his loot near his farm in the abandoned mines area. To blackmail him, you must get the property of the Governor.
#subobj  1
Find the farm
The farm upon which the relatives of Baldie live is located on the western shore of the large lake. To get there, first go to the southern shore, then west. Exercise caution: you will be met not only by the criminal family but also by the snow tigers which are trained on the farm.
#subobj  2
Find the barn and the hiding place
The hiding place of the loot is in the barn located in the northern part of the valley where the farm lies. Another landmark is two stacks of wood which stand on either side of the barn.
#subobj  3
Take the box with the collection
You should take the loot from the barn.
